<project xml:id="cool-reflexionaSobreElVolumenLiquido" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Reflexiona sobre el volumen líquido</title>

<statement>
  <p>¿Qué aprendiste sobre el volumen líquido y sobre cómo medirlo?</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: Liquid volume is the amount of space that a liquid takes up. It can be hard to compare the liquid volume that containers hold if we don’t use the same unit. Liters are units of liquid volume.</p>
  </solution>


